ll adapt the data to match this key request. My main focus is on the specific instructions I was given.\n\n\n**Adding New Plans**\n\nI\'m now incorporating several new plans, including \"Cabelo e Barba 2x por M\303\252s,\" \"PREMIUM,\" \"WEEK,\" and \"Barba Ilimitado\" with their respective pricing, descriptions, features, and checkout URLs. I\'m focusing on their data structure integration into the current project.\n\n\n**Structuring New Plans**\n\nI\'m now integrating the \"Plano DUO,\" \"Plano ONE,\" \"Careca Club,\" and \"BASIC\" plans, each with their associated pricing, descriptions, features, and checkout URLs. I\'m carefully organizing these new offerings to ensure they\'re correctly incorporated into the existing data structure.\n\n\n**Adding More Plans**\n\nI\'m currently adding the \"BASIC - Ter\303\247a-Feira - Corte\" plan, priced at 99.90, along with the \"COMBO ONE - Corte e Barba 1x no M\303\252s\" plan at 109.90. I\'m also including new plans specific to Unidade Bela Vista, starting with the \"VIP - COMBO - HOR\303\201RIO FIXO\" plan at 250.00 and the \"SMART - 2 Cortes e 2 Barbas\" plan at 159.90. I\'m focused on detailed integration.\n\n\n**Finalizing New Plan Updates**\n\nI\'m now adding the \"CABELO E BARBA ILIMITADO\" plan at 180.00 to include Corte, Barba, and Raspado. I am adding \"BARBA ILIMITADA\" at 99.90. This will allow for Corte and Barba with unlimited services. I am making sure the data structure is complete. I am also making sure that these plans can be easily integrated.\n\n\n**Adding Bela Vista Specific Plans**\n\nI\'m currently focused on adding plans exclusively for the Bela Vista location. I\'ve just integrated \"BARBA ILIMITADA (Bela Vista)\" at 119.90, \"ONE - 1 Corte por M\303\252s\" at 40.00, \"COMBO ONE - 1 Corte + Barba por M\303\252s\" at 85.00, and \"CARECA CLUB\" at 69.90. These all include features like \"Sem taxa ades\303\243o\" and \"Cancele quando quiser.\" I\'m also ensuring the correct image URLs and checkout URLs