ating Social Media Icons**\n\nI\'m now incorporating Instagram and Facebook icons into the footer using `lucide-react`, focusing on adding them to the import statement. I\'ll then move on to adding them to the footer section, to replace the existing copyright statement. I\'m focusing on ensuring seamless integration with the existing design and maintaining responsiveness.\n\n\n"
